workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
It's phase 3, so let's see how much your chest can handle.


Get your form right with the exercise tutorial before adding weight.


If you want to cool down after working out, you'll find the link to stretching sessions at the top of each week of workouts.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: Find your intensity and get your chest ready to work.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: You'll be doing a lot of reps in supersets, so stay focused. Don't let your form slip.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: Target your pecs from all angles.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: Alternate flys and plank holds for major muscle activation.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Go out strong with descending sets of dips.
